        <updateDate>2021-03-31T15:50:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>COVID-19 Safer Detention Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill modifies programs that allow for early release of certain federal inmates, including by expanding eligibility for the Elderly Home Detention Pilot Program and making vulnerability to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) a basis for compassionate release during the public health emergency.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
